title: PresiTrendial Inauguration 1/19: QAnon, Dodger Stadium, Kyrie Irving, Presidential Pardons
itunes:title: PresiTrendial Inauguration 1/19: QAnon, Dodger Stadium, Kyrie Irving, Presidential Pardons
description:
On this edition of PresiTrendial Inauguration Jack and Miles discuss what QAnon thinks is going to happen tomorrow, Dodger Stadium being converted to a COVID vaccine site, Kyrie Irving doing good work with his money during the pandemic, and the many pardons the president is about to hand out on his last day in office.
